{"tid":41233,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"約左聽日洗牙 緊張到成晚都訓唔著","createTime":"2016-12-15T17:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T18:40:12.000Z","uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10b75ade065fcfc630053d2e9cbc94d0f54dcf96","tid":41233,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的 前日我行行下街 經過一間牙醫診所 見到有個靚女大波姐姐係門口講野<br />\n佢前面講個堆野我就聽唔到 一行埋去就聽到<br />\n<br />\n靚女姐姐話: 洗唔洗牙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢對面個男人就答佢: 你咪牙醫啊助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次都多得你唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 省到我立立令<br />\n<br />\n我心諗 原來個姐姐係牙醫黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又靚又叻 仲洗牙可以洗到咁乾淨 真係人間少有啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姐姐: 咁點啊 唔滿意咪再黎囉 但你今次洗唔洗牙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來仲有售後服務咁撚正 我都想洗牙啊唔係講笑<br />\n<br />\n我就行埋去舉晒手答: 我洗我洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後日3點 OK?<br />\n<br />\n個姐姐呆一呆望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你洗? <br />\n<br />\n我答: 係啊係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就走左<br />\n<br />\n聽日又見到個靚女大波姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起都興奮 唔知會唔會有AV情節呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊張到成晚都訓唔著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5008434fe62e082ff4321e11e19c0c7c3dac0c2","tid":41233,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"訓啦，過兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef90f2a4abd3c4405007e40bde860c3902e0e1f","tid":41233,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2